# Verify browser exceptions via curl (required)

When the developer provides a **URL** and reports a **clear exception visible in the browser** (PHP fatal, stack trace, error banner), do not claim a fix is working until it is verified.

## Rule (guardrail)

- For non-doc changes, run `setup:di:compile` at the end of the task.
- Do not claim a fix works until it is verified.

## Runbook

See `curl-exception-verification` skill.
